The paper focuses on assisting graphical user interface (UI) layout design, which is a task related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, specifically Transformer-based tree decoders, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper proposes new metrics for measuring the accuracy of tree prediction, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG).
